attributes.short-description: Covers individuals or small businesses with up to 100 employees
attributes.name: Personal/Small Business License
attributes.details:
Includes Font Awesome Pro (1,000+ icons and SVG framework) plus ALL Kickstarter stretch goals:

  • 46 additional icon packs
  • JavaScript component packages for React, Angular, Ember.js, and Vue.js
  • Exclusive access to the Font Awesome Community + Icon Voting
  • 600 duotone icons
  • Font Awesome Pro CDN free for one year
  • iOS + Android support
  • Additional thin icon style
  • Desktop icon subsetter
  • Design plugins for Illustrator, Photoshop, & Sketch
  • “Designing an Awesome Icon Set” eBook

Personal / Small Business License Details

  • Covers individuals or small businesses with up to 100 employees.
  • License follows the person or business.
  • If the project is for personal use, the person should have a license. If the project is for a business, the business should have a license.
  • Use on as many projects (web app/site, iOS app, etc.) as you like.
  • Don’t use in a theme or re-distribute.
  • License is transferable.
  • For greater than 100 employees, buy multiple small business licenses. Enterprise licenses are available for up to 3,000 employees.

Student / Non-Profit License Details

  • Covers individual students OR non-profit (501C3) organizations of any size.

  • Use on as many projects (web app/site, iOS app, etc.) as you like.
  • Don’t use in a theme or re-distribute.
  • License is transferrable to another student or non-profit!

attributes.details:
Includes Font Awesome Pro (1,000+ icons and SVG framework) plus ALL Kickstarter stretch goals:

attributes.short-description: Allows use in a single theme that you can re-sell. For multiple themes, buy multiple theme licenses.
attributes.name: Theme License
attributes.details:
Theme License Details

  • Allows use in a single theme that you can re-sell. For multiple themes, buy multiple theme licenses.
  • Cannot re-distribute Font Awesome Pro except embedded in your theme.
  • Grants a single personal / small business license for theme buyer to use Font Awesome Pro as a part of your theme (not outside).
  • For the buyers of your theme, this license includes all Font Awesome Pro icons, Stretch Goal icons, and CSS and SVG frameworks, but does not include additional stretch goal rewards.
  • Also includes one Personal / Small Business License for your own use.

attributes.short-description: 1 year subscription to all updates, icons, and Pro services offerred.
attributes.name: Standard
attributes.details:
Font Awesome Pro Standard Yearly Subscription

A perpetual license and a year of updates and services. This subscription will renew automatically.

A license is based on the number of individual users, or seats, who have access to Font Awesome Pro. That means a 10 seat license would mean that up to 10 people (like say your design and dev teams) can use us in their hands-on work.

attributes.short-description: 1 year subscription to all updates, icons, and Pro services for one student only.
attributes.name: Student
attributes.details:
Font Awesome Pro Student Yearly Subscription

A perpetual license and a year of updates and services. This subscription will renew automatically.

For as long as you are a student, this license will cover all of the classroom and side projects you can come up with. Once you graduate, grab a standard license with a discount on us!
